<p>(I'm posting this comment ahead of the beginning of the voting period because I don't want to forget later.)</p>
<p>So, as you might have guessed, this tale features my own <a href="/scp-306">SCP-306</a> and DStecks's <a href="/scp-659">SCP-659</a>. There are also four other skips from the contest eligible articles mentioned at the beginning of the tale. These skips happened to be some of my favorites, which is why they are included.</p>
<p>This is actually the longest story I have ever written (aside from a horrifically awful tale I wrote way back in 4th grade). I'm pretty happy with how it turned out.</p>
<p>Happy reading!</p>

